find . -name  → Traditional search

📂 DIRECTORY OPERATIONS
mkcd <name>   → Create and enter directory
ls / eza      → List with icons and git status
tree / lt     → Show directory tree

💡 PRO TIPS
• Use 'z' instead of 'cd' - it learns your habits!
• Press Tab for auto-completion
• Use wildcards: *.txt, **/*.js"
}

